      "rationale": "Testing was conducted exclusively under the standard ASTM F1717 compression-bending configuration at a single load angle and displacement rate. No variation in test boundary conditions, load angle, or displacement rate was explored. The required Gradation 3 demands at least two distinct test condition variants to bound the model prediction space; only a single condition was employed. Gradation 2 achieved against a required Gradation 3. This shortfall was documented during assessment and accepted on the basis that the COU is narrowly scoped to the F1717 standard test, and the single condition is directly representative of the intended regulatory submission context."
